+Copy and organize master calibration frames from source to an organized library based on FITS/XISF header metadata.
+
+## Overview
+
+This tool organizes master calibration frames (bias, dark, flat) into a structured library. It:
+
+- Scans source directories for master calibration frames (XISF and FITS formats)
+- Extracts metadata from FITS headers to determine frame type and properties
+- Copies frames to destination organized by type and camera
+- Names files with full metadata for traceability
+- Creates date-based subdirectories for flats
+
